{"tid":901883,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺四季煲仔飯真係比人吹大左好多?","createTime":"2018-11-14T10:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T08:07:13.000Z","uid":68626,"like":101,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9b3bbcbd88b02bf033f4f67cf5a85ddbfd496b","tid":901883,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T10:59:48.000Z","msg":"等位：八點左右去到門口，條龍長撚到仆街<br />\n令我等二人不禁萌生退意，作食隔壁檔口打算<br />\n但稍作觀察發現條龍都去得好快，大約三十人排隊，等左二十分鐘左右就到<br />\n差唔多排到你個陣就會比餐牌你叫你落單，難怪條龍去得咁快<br />\n環境：差撚到仆街，Ｄ位好撚窄，個場本身都大，但係放左勁多凳，都係個句，難怪條龍去得咁快，基本上都係要答台，樓主一男一女食都係岩岩夠位坐，兩個肥仔去既話就祝你好運，基本上無私隱可言，連隔離台保險狗係到ＳＥＬＬ野都聽撚到晒<br />\n服務：Ｍ記級數<br />\n食物：叫左兩個煲仔飯，鳳爪排骨同滑雞<br />\n排骨好撚多骨，接近無肉，鳳爪得一隻爪屌你老母，當我狗呀？<br />\n滑雞臘腸不過不失，但唔值排隊同名氣，番去樓下食盅頭飯二十蚊個同佢差唔多ＬＶ<br />\n頂盡大快活級數，每個飯６５蚊，另加４６蚊兩塊蠔餅，蠔餅都幾好食，可以再屌<br />\n<br />\n結語：一個大話多人講就可能會變真，就好似真係有人當謝霆鋒做廚師咁，間野咁撚樣都可以出名，唔撚係掛，４０蚊都要諗諗，屌你老母"},{"pid":"f0d5839981a7857134ee637cc68b0e43629f3a97","tid":901883,"uid":56328,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T11:30:53.000Z","msg":"啲餸幾好食，飯就一時時，但依家真係好撚貴，大概7，8年前23蚊雙拼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab123aa1bed29e8593f7557c95d60c2f2276f919","tid":901883,"uid":28761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"依家不了"},{"pid":"be524a359e6e818e64884eb740f73703ae0e886c","tid":901883,"uid":195089,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T11:56:18.000Z","msg":"去開興記，好少去一間唔係連鎖嘅餐廳咁多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b2687be11b663b4fc3406d72e8aedf646d1a5d","tid":901883,"uid":49216,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:32:00.000Z","msg":"貴左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇住佢廿幾，四十幾，<br />\n早排行過「嘩，唔撚係呀，六十幾」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0910b0cddf91239a7acd7dac617d9feec39ba1f9","tid":901883,"uid":139676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:34:29.000Z","msg":"大陸人先食"},{"pid":"b41fd46e974d83de7c876ab3d92277655a0b7da8","tid":901883,"uid":40908,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:35:08.000Z","msg":"四季同興記都係垃圾<br />\n廣州d煲仔飯好食好多"},{"pid":"86ec65f86d13627faf97e15806c0f06223a9934e","tid":901883,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:36:12.000Z","msg":"環境惡劣 overprice 野食一般"},{"pid":"74477c2254eb33697ea159c6416db81cf18ae3ca","tid":901883,"uid":74278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:41:21.000Z","msg":"大快活肉餅煲仔飯我覺得其實ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa15e51de42fdeb643096cdf218e6a4f4bf9fba","tid":901883,"uid":13644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:43:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾黎"},{"pid":"4bcb18086f69aa79b8681c84d0ff4404b20f1138","tid":901883,"uid":162539,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"邊度煲仔飯好食？<br />\n<br />\n西環坤記屌唔屌得過？"},{"pid":"039fdd75b44c56552c0999cb1a680a1273bda888","tid":901883,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:44:52.000Z","msg":"十年前又平又好食"},{"pid":"205f1fd7a8452e0c0dfb307379aaa4bfe65fefbc","tid":901883,"uid":96708,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4bcb18086f69aa79b8681c84d0ff4404b20f1138","tid":901883,"uid":162539,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"邊度煲仔飯好食？<br />\n<br />\n西環坤記屌唔屌得過？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T13:45:03.000Z","msg":"識食一定食坤記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n白鱔煲仔飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b7622b47738c8078e22b857cbcc0ca1d4c2aef","tid":901883,"uid":37757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T13:46:37.000Z","msg":"四季比狗食 <br />\n次次行過都指住條隊黎笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c31f65488509f68d6139a521e8337f13abe056","tid":901883,"uid":36670,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T13:49:18.000Z","msg":"個人意見覺得西九food court果間平平地又唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc05f6195443e5db0c9708b40479ee27a45c931","tid":901883,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"be524a359e6e818e64884eb740f73703ae0e886c","tid":901883,"uid":195089,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T11:56:18.000Z","msg":"去開興記，好少去一間唔係連鎖嘅餐廳咁多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T13:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 四季坐係溫室食乜撚煲仔飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n緊係坐街邊開支啤酒最爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425783e14f13280dd4fb71272f076c3eeaf15c04","tid":901883,"uid":170375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"吹大左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f0f6d5a5142f335459d086200e6caed2a53673","tid":901883,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T13:55:58.000Z","msg":"幾年前 食過1次<br />\n環境好差，迫，坐得唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食物我覺得麻麻 記得份量唔多 總之唔會飽 <br />\n印象中蠔餅係Ok<br />\n<br />\n呢間野 食完一次就無下次<br />\n食一次當吹水話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完全係以前唔知點解出名(可能以前真係好食)<br />\n&gt;多人食&gt;更出名&gt;更多人食的Circle"},{"pid":"f63eaa24312301d45f66b96ee760b6f609c826aa","tid":901883,"uid":149487,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T13:58:05.000Z","msg":"真心介紹紹華小廚 係筲箕灣<br />\n我住新界都會突登搭車入去食"},{"pid":"76f384cf8c1aea9dd263f4e371ff254df3b96c9e","tid":901883,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"加撚到6x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍拖果陣同老婆去先廿幾"},{"pid":"66cddf2118ee2428c049e3171204e55176137fab","tid":901883,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76f384cf8c1aea9dd263f4e371ff254df3b96c9e","tid":901883,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"加撚到6x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拍拖果陣同老婆去先廿幾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"好撚多遊客/團食<br />\n<br />\n再加20 都塞滿人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60bd9458103a9b8632c586a6119d20e8cf67b7b","tid":901883,"uid":6211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:09:27.000Z","msg":"不嬲以前係出名'平'唔係出名好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6d21c3fd40fede4c0943f6ff9aac00395bf707","tid":901883,"uid":72481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:20:38.000Z","msg":"興記都係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n講好食，好景對面有好似叫好好味之類咁ge名"},{"pid":"012a7d02e8410aed740d07a3c6daf7deaffc362e","tid":901883,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:28:24.000Z","msg":"試過屌佢<br />\n一打開得幾粒肉<br />\n不過果陣廿幾蚊算鳩數<br />\n依家咁嘅價錢<br />\n使撚食佢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64d5b8f898b7188fd52ddbc65a2d18e8e4cb7c8","tid":901883,"uid":10844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T14:28:44.000Z","msg":"香港人食野係睇邊度俾人吹奏就去食㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n服務質素都係其次"}]}